BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:zk6j8UysAONliFHw22SKr
SUMMARY:Comedy of Love: A Valentine's Day Improv
DTSTAMP:20260214T003616Z
DTSTART:20260213T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Looking for a Valentine’s Day plan that’s as unpredictable as l
	ove itself? Don’t miss The Comedy of Love – a side-splitting\\\, heart-thr
	obbing improv show that will have you laughing\\\, blushing\\\, and maybe 
	even swooning! Watch as real-life couples from our talented ensemble turn 
	your wild suggestions into unscripted tales of passion\\\, heartbreak\\\, 
	and everything in between. Whether it’s your first date or a solo adventur
	e\\\, this one-of-a-kind night promises endless laughs and plenty of “aww”
	 moments. \\nJoin us at our cozy theater nestled by the iconic Gum Wall in
	 the romantic Pike Place Market – because nothing says “love” like comedy 
	in one of Seattle’s most charming spots!\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/comedy-of-love-a-valentines
	-day-improv-3/2026-02-13/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:tp1h7yN-JEOcAekwcYO0T
SUMMARY:I Saw You: A Comedy with Heart VALENTINE'S SPECIAL
DTSTAMP:20260214T003616Z
DTSTART:20260213T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:This Valentine’s weekend\\\, Unexpected Productions turns misse
	d connections into unexpected sparks with a special edition of I Saw U. In
	spired by Seattle’s favorite alt-weekly section from The Stranger (and cla
	ssic Craigslist Missed Connections)\\\, this hilarious and heartfelt impro
	v show imagines what really happens when those almost-lovers finally meet.
	 \\nWatch our performers bring the quirkiest\\\, sweetest\\\, and most out
	rageous listings to life\\\, taking them from first glance to first date—a
	nd beyond. Whether you’re coupled up\\\, flying solo\\\, or proudly cynica
	l about love\\\, you’ll laugh\\\, cringe\\\, and maybe even swoon as fanta
	sy collides with reality. \\nCelebrate love in all its awkward\\\, hopeful
	\\\, chaotic glory with a night of big laughs\\\, tender moments\\\, and r
	omantic surprises—only on February 13 & 14 at the Market Theater in Pike P
	lace Market.\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/i-saw-you-a-comedy-with-hea
	rt-8-2/2026-02-13/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:0JCCtnSo8Pvpoqy3iYXVH
SUMMARY:Seattle Theatresports Valentine's Show
DTSTAMP:20260214T003616Z
DTSTART:20260213T213000Z
DESCRIPTION:Turn Valentine’s weekend into a laugh-fueled date night with Se
	attle Theatresports\\\, Seattle’s most electric improv battle—special Vale
	ntine’s shows on 2/13 & 2/14. It’s fast\\\, funny\\\, and wildly unpredict
	able\\\, with your suggestions shaping every moment. \\nWelcome to Seattle
	’s funnest improv comedy experience at Unexpected Productions inside the M
	arket Theater. Two teams of top improvisers go head-to-head in a no-holds-
	barred comedy showdown—part game night\\\, part sporting event\\\, and 100
	% powered by the crowd. Boo the judges. Cheer the Gum Wall race. Laugh ’ti
	l it hurts. \\nNo scripts. No safety nets. Just bold choices\\\, quick thi
	nking\\\, and joyful chaos. Whether you’re bringing a date\\\, a friend\\\
	, or your own romantic skepticism\\\, this is Valentine’s weekend with edg
	e\\\, energy\\\, and a whole lot of heart. \\nFri. & Sat. | 9:30 PM | Febr
	uary 13 & 14Love is unpredictable. Comedy should be too.\n\nFrom Unexpecte
	d Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-theatresports-2026-
	2/2026-02-13/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
