BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:s4dobxAeKWZYimbNmK1Qb
SUMMARY:Duo Comedy Showcase 2026
DTSTAMP:20260214T003616Z
DTSTART:20260218T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle’s one and only open mic dedicated to two-person improv 
	teams! Every week at Unexpected Productions\\\, two-person teams take the 
	stage to create hilarious\\\, fast-paced\\\, totally unscripted comedy rig
	ht before your eyes. No scripts\\\, no safety nets—just pure improv magic.
	 \\nAt Duos\\\, everyone shines. Newer performers sharpen their game. Seas
	oned improvisers experiment\\\, take risks\\\, and get wonderfully weird. 
	The results? Quick-witted scenes\\\, surprising twists\\\, and bold choice
	s that feel impossible until you watch them happen live. \\nWhether you dr
	eam of being the next Key & Peele\\\, Tina Fey & Amy Poehler\\\, or a chao
	tic tag-team like Deadpool & Wolverine\\\, this is your chance to take the
	 mic and run with it. All experience levels are welcome. Bring a friend\\\
	, form a team\\\, and give Seattle a show they won’t forget. To sign up yo
	ur duo\\\, email duoshowcase@gmail.com. \\nLooking for a midweek serotonin
	 boost? Watching the show is just as fun as performing in it. Grab a seat\
	\\, grab a friend\\\, and discover why Unexpected Productions is the home 
	of Seattle improv.\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/duo-comedy-showcase-2026/20
	26-02-18/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:BN7X3TJ4kZVuSUNXCWENz
SUMMARY:Loose Cannons 2026
DTSTAMP:20260214T003616Z
DTSTART:20260219T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Loose Cannons is Seattle improv at its most unpredictable. Ever
	y performance at Unexpected Productions in Pike Place Market is a one-of-a
	-kind experience: exciting\\\, unexpected\\\, a little dangerous\\\, and a
	lways ridiculously fun. This is the show where anything can happen and usu
	ally does. \\nPart One: Part One: The night kicks off with a unique perfor
	mance\\\, setting the performers in a new format with special guest improv
	isers showcasing their signature style or a never-before-seen format. Your
	 suggestions fuel the fire\\\, and the improvisers will ignite the stage\\
	\, bringing your ideas to life. \\nPart Two: The second half launches from
	 a single audience suggestion\\\, setting the performers in motion. It mig
	ht start with a song\\\, a monologue\\\, or a rapid-fire group connection 
	game. Whatever emerges will inspire spontaneous stories\\\, surprising twi
	sts\\\, and big comedic swings. \\nLoose Cannons is fueled by audience ide
	as\\\, fearless performers\\\, and the thrill of not knowing what happens 
	next. You light the fuse. They run with it. What they create is entirely u
	p to you.\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/loose-cannons-2026/2026-02-
	19/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
